          MaskType      "PI Controller Digital"
          MaskDescription "This is a Digital Controller with PI algorith, Anti"
"Winding-Up protection and FeedForward. To use this block you need to insert t"
"he parameters of the  standar parallel continuous form of a PI Controller:\n"
"\t\t     Gc(s) = Kp + Ki/s\n"
"Notes:\n"
"*This is a \"Digital Controller\" so a sample time Ts is required.\n"
"*If you do not use limits to control, put \"inf\" in the Limit box. "
          MaskDisplay   "Icon:line({-18,-18,22},{-10,10,10})\n"
"Icon:color(255, 0, 0)\n"
